    "body": "<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-11-30 at 12 24 14\" src=\"https://github.com/starship/starship/assets/114588139/fb63de9b-3dec-48c8-b8cb-ea24e00c6641\">\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-11-30 at 12 24 33\" src=\"https://github.com/starship/starship/assets/114588139/4d22cb66-93b9-41b8-b697-faca8723b069\">\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-11-30 at 12 24 43\" src=\"https://github.com/starship/starship/assets/114588139/17b4b1eb-655c-4602-be4c-202ae78dfc84\">\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-11-30 at 12 24 50\" src=\"https://github.com/starship/starship/assets/114588139/ca952f01-e210-44f6-9701-c2cf3586e77d\">\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-11-30 at 12 24 53\" src=\"https://github.com/starship/starship/assets/114588139/b39c432c-e337-4ad1-8721-e7eb29eb5c61\">\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-11-30 at 12 25 02\" src=\"https://github.com/starship/starship/assets/114588139/344b3868-ca3c-4b5f-9b7a-e7e392df60cb\">\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-11-30 at 12 25 06\" src=\"https://github.com/starship/starship/assets/114588139/ee70bfc0-4b17-4511-9792-2c9ba860e3d6\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nwhen i ran the command \"exec starship\" the shell switched my user to root, even though the root user is disabled on my system. restarting the machine seemed to fix the issue though. it is noteworthy that i enabled and then disabled the root user on my system right before this bug occurred. after the restart i wasn't able to reproduce the bug (although i haven't tried to enable and disenable the root user again).",
